java.io.Serializable
public class DtoStatusException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException

An exception that indicates that a Data Transfer Object (DTO) violates a constraint. The exception contains a list of the parameters for the error message; the final display of the message should include generating the string with the parameters. You can get the list of parameter strings and determine how many parameters there are by the length of the list.

Author:
Robert J. Muller
